{"tid":242000,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"手動關閉 Port 135/445","createTime":"2017-05-13T14:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T07:43:38.000Z","uid":70008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39d313fe5de1c62cbf0c4f7c599fb2f2a7e9626f","tid":242000,"uid":70008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"手動關閉 Port 135 <br />\n<br />\nClick Start, click All Programs, and then click Accessories.<br />\n<strong><strong>Right-click</strong></strong> Command prompt, and then click Run as administrator.<br />\n<br />\n輸入<br />\nnetsh advfirewall firewall add rule dir=in action=block protocol=TCP localport=135 name=&quot;Block_TCP-135&quot;<br />\n<br />\nClick Enter.<br />\n<br />\n輸入<br />\nnetsh advfirewall firewall add rule dir=in action=block protocol=TCP localport=445 name=&quot;Block_TCP-445&quot;<br />\n<br />\nClick Enter.<br />\n<br />\n如果佢寫&quot;ok.&quot; 咁就即係閂咗"},{"pid":"d0f35405b436727014b1ad58da197f2bef248028","tid":242000,"uid":7245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"等巴打覆"},{"pid":"dddb5bcb1fa1c498802c8d11bff42bde8b747232","tid":242000,"uid":6717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:16:16.000Z","msg":"關左會點？ 電腦白痴"},{"pid":"11f32661e64da1cb6d03d0547e8d8fc872f940a6","tid":242000,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關左會點？ 電腦白痴</blockquote><br />\n呢兩個本身公廁port黎，熄左都冇影響<br />\n135係用黎遠程搖控<br />\n445係用黎share野，例如printer,file<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個port比人發現太多漏洞，已經比人棄用左，不過個windows其實冇停用到，所以hacker依家就係透過漏洞入你部電腦搖控鎖file"},{"pid":"445651f2dd471fc9ff1d999886b46bf8befa1241","tid":242000,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:04:36.000Z","msg":"用緊其他防毒，Windows本身嗰個firewall已經閂咗，如果防毒冇特別嘢可以set，係咪只可以相信佢？<br />\n<br />\n用緊bitdefender total security 2017。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/272FQnh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"